title: Kirk Minihane Grows the Team
description:
Former/interim producer and salesman extraordinaire Dave Cullinane returns with one last pitch to join the Kirk Minihane Show. Minihane does his best to instigate civil war amongst his minions.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
